Bitcoinmarket24.com offers Bitcoins 24/7 - anytime during any day. The service is convenient, safe and fast. If you are using instant SEPA you will have your Bitcoins within less than one minute. No lenghty registration process, no unavailability, just a simple, fast and secure way to order Bitcoins.

At the moment traditional SEPA and instant SEPA are offered as payment methods but it is planned to expand the payment methods.

Instant SEPA is available for the following countries:

* Austria
* Belgium
* Germany
* Netherlands
* Switzerland

This service was announced on December 30, 2011 (1.1).

